#: ../../content/news/2026-03-08_02.10.00.md:1
msgid "2.10 (2026-03-08)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/news/2026-03-08_02.10.00.md:3
msgid "Lint False-Positive Corrections"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/news/2026-03-08_02.10.00.md:5
msgid ""
"With the newly added linter support, a series of package/VCS type checks "
"(RT105-RT113) resulted in false-positive events when package definitions use"
" non-constant value for select configuration entries. This release includes "
"a series of improvements towards the detection of these types to help reduce"
" the chance of these warnings being generated."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/news/2026-03-08_02.10.00.md:11
msgid "Support for CycloneDX SBOM Generation"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/news/2026-03-08_02.10.00.md:13
msgid ""
"Support has been added for generating [CycloneDX][cyclonedx]-compatible "
"software build of materials (SBOM) documents. This includes CycloneDX v1.7 "
"JSON and XML compatible documents."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/news/2026-03-08_02.10.00.md:17
msgid "API Mode"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/news/2026-03-08_02.10.00.md:19
msgid ""
"This release introduces a new [API mode](/guides/api-mode). Callers can now "
"trigger releng-tool with the `--api` argument to have the standard output "
"stream generate a programmatic response (JSON) for scripts/etc. to use."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/news/2026-03-08_02.10.00.md:23
msgid "API response data is limited at this time."
msgstr ""

